// load/add/store replaces x64's LOCK XADD. The root GT (main) is created via
// __gt_spawn_root, which never bumps the counter, so the first `async` spawn
// gets id 1. __gt_trace_emit self-gates on __at_trace_enabled, so this is a
// cheap no-op for non-trace builds. Mirrors the spawn-trace tail of
